<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBBFF9A645CFB94FED4FBC1" bold="true" box="[113,261,1099,1122]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">
<typeStatus id="5C61884FFFBBFF9A645CFB94FF78FBC1" box="[113,169,1099,1122]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Type</typeStatus>
species.
</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFBBFF9A6521FB94FD71FBC1" authority="Kaszab, 1981" authorityName="Kaszab" authorityYear="1981" box="[268,672,1099,1122]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Indochillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="andamanus">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBBFF9A6521FB94FDD4FBC1" box="[268,517,1099,1122]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Indochillus andamanus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E74B4B1CFFBBFF9A6621FB94FD71FBC1" author="KASZAB Z." box="[524,672,1099,1122]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" pagination="273 - 313" refId="ref12775" refString="KASZAB Z. 1981: Neue orientalische Stenosini (Coleoptera: Tenebrionidae). Acta Zoologica Academiae Scientiarum Hungaricae 27: 273 - 313." type="journal article" year="1981">Kaszab, 1981</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, here designated.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="CBC06566FFBBFF9A645CFBA5FE1FFB52" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" type="description">
<paragraph id="836536EDFFBBFF9A645CFBA5FE1FFB52" blockId="11.[113,1089,1146,1553]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBBFF9A645CFBA5FF2DFB32" bold="true" box="[113,252,1146,1169]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Description.</emphasis>
Body length 3.9–5.0 mm. Clypeus straight, without tooth. Tempora shorter than eye length. Suborbital keel reduced. Occiput very slightly flattened. Junction of interval 7 and 9 on elytra forming small obliquely directed humeral corner (
<figureCitation id="1BE12A68FFBBFF9A671FFB65FC53FB72" box="[818,898,1210,1233]" captionStart="Figs 10–16. 10–12" captionStartId="14.[151,187,1490,1509]" captionTargetBox="[197,1080,222,1472]" captionTargetId="figure-10@14.[197,1080,219,1472]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="Figs 10–16. 10–12 – dorsal view:10 – Pseudochillus (Micropseudochillus) palawanus sp.nov., holotype♂, Philippines (Palawan); 11 – P.(M.) thailandicus sp. nov., holotype ♂, Thailand.; 12 – P.(M.) indochinensis sp. nov., paratype ♀, Vietnam. 13 – P.(M.) indochinensis sp. nov., tooth on clypeus; 14–15 – humeral corner: 14 – P.(Kaszabochillus) helferi sp. nov.; 15 – P.(Pseudochillus) bangaloreanus (Kaszab, 1981). 16 – P.(P.) bangaloreanus (Kaszab, 1981), punctures on epipleura. Scale bar = 4 mm (Figs 10–12)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5304655" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5304655/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Fig. 14</figureCitation>
). Elytra glabrous. Antennomeres longer than wide.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="CBC06566FFBBFF9A645CFB25FEF8FA12" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="836536EDFFBBFF9A645CFB25FEF8FA12" blockId="11.[113,1089,1146,1553]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBBFF9A645CFB25FF39FAB2" bold="true" box="[113,232,1274,1297]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFBBFF9A64C2FB25FE44FAB2" authority="Fouquè, 2015" authorityName="Fouquè" authorityYear="2015" box="[239,405,1274,1297]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" rank="subGenus" status="subgen. nov." subGenus="Kaszabochillus">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBBFF9A64C2FB25FE44FAB2" box="[239,405,1274,1297]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Kaszabochillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="AA9D5784FFBBFF9A65B1FB25FDF4FAB2" box="[412,549,1274,1297]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" rank="subGenus">subgen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is characterized by straight clypeus without tooth (remaining subgenera have concave clypeus with small tooth); glabrous elytra and presence of small obliquely directed humeral corners (
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFBBFF9A664BFAE5FCECFAF2" authority="Fouquè, 2015" authorityName="Fouquè" authorityYear="2015" box="[614,829,1338,1361]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" rank="subGenus" status="subgen. nov." subGenus="Micropseudochillus">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBBFF9A664BFAE5FCECFAF2" box="[614,829,1338,1361]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Micropseudochillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="AA9D5784FFBBFF9A676BFAE5FC01FAF2" box="[838,976,1338,1361]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" rank="subGenus">subgen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
possesses row of setae on elytral intervals 1, 3, 5, 7 and 9); elytra without humeral corner; and tempora shorter than eye length (
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFBBFF9A6580FAA5FD97FA32" authority="Fouquè, 2015" authorityName="Fouquè" authorityYear="2015" box="[429,582,1402,1425]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" rank="subGenus" status="subgen. nov." subGenus="Pseudochillus">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBBFF9A6580FAA5FD97FA32" box="[429,582,1402,1425]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Pseudochillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="AA9D5784FFBBFF9A6661FAA5FD05FA32" box="[588,724,1402,1425]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" rank="subGenus">subgen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
has tempora 1.5–2.0 times longer than eye length).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="CBC06566FFBBFF9A645CFA65FF34F9B2" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="836536EDFFBBFF9A645CFA65FF34F9B2" blockId="11.[113,1089,1146,1553]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBBFF9A645CFA65FF23FA72" bold="true" box="[113,242,1466,1489]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Etymology.</emphasis>
The new subgenus is named in honor of Dr. Zoltán Kaszab (1915–1986), expert in 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFBBFF9A64A6FA05FEF7FA52" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[139,294,1498,1521]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Tenebrionidae</taxonomicName>
, and the name is derived from his surname and genus 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFBBFF9A677AFA05FC3CFA52" authority="Fouquè, 2015" authorityName="Fouquè" authorityYear="2015" box="[855,1005,1498,1521]" genus="Pseudochillus" pageId="11" pageNumber="226" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBBFF9A677AFA05FC3CFA52" box="[855,1005,1498,1521]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Pseudochillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, gender masculine.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
